text: Santo António (Portuguese for "Saint Anthony") is a parish in the district of Ponta Delgada in the Azores. The population in 2011 was 1,829,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of 11.75 km².Eurostat It is located in the northwestern part of the island of São Miguel. ==References== Category:Parishes of Ponta Delgada
title: Santo António (Ponta Delgada)
